I"c<h3 id="wcag-what">WCAG what?</h3>

<p>The Web Content and Accessibility Guidelines are provided as a means to create more accessible interfaces for all, especially those with visual impairment.</p>

<h3 id="instant">Instant</h3>

<p>The entire app UI updates instantly when picking colors, making it easy to get the color contrast information you need to make informed decisions about the color of your text.</p>

<h3 id="guess-no-more">Guess no more</h3>

<p>With this app you can see the contrast score as soon as colors are picked. No more disrupting your design flow by going online to check contrast.</p>
